	(text "SEC A  CONTROLLER (mains-side domain, DGND): Teensy 4.1 + TFT/touch + buttons. Ethernet = PJRC Ethernet Kit on Teensy bottom pads. Floating +5V_An arrives from linear PSU at J6."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 25.4 -8.636 0)
		(effects
