				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "8721a755-33c0-4b80-9b48-9a35d856d9d8")
	)
	(text "SEC B  ISOLATION BARRIER: U2 SPI+control, U3/U4 relay coils + ADC readback. Left of chips = DGND/+3V3 domain, right = STAR/+5V_An floating domain. Keep >=6mm creepage under U2-U4."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 25.146 -4.318 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.6 1.6)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "9adedddc-93e6-4cec-97dc-864f52cf12fe")
	)
	(text "level 1 = trickle 330R only (~1.2mA); each added branch 150R/68R/33R/15R => ~4/10/22/48mA. Gate LOW = branch ON."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 26.416 116.332 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
