		(uuid "a1516dd4-4d3b-40d8-8e9d-dc132c4be667")
	)
	(text "(3) Floating-domain logic is 5V; Teensy side 3.3V via isolators. (4) Analog +/-12V goes to FE J2 only; STAR commons join at the FE board."
